libt3
------------------------------------------
t3 is a lightweight thread pool for C++.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.4-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  libt3-devel-1.0.0-1bl2
  libt3_1-1.0.0-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.37.2-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/c9s/t3

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/c9s/t3/archive/refs/tags/1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libt3-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libt3-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libt3-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libt3-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libt3_1-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libt3-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libt3)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libt3.README
  /usr/share/doc/libt3/README.md

(libt3_1)
  /usr/bin/cygt3-1.dll

(libt3-devel)
  /usr/include/t3/channel.h
  /usr/include/t3/thread_pool.h
  /usr/include/t3/thread_task.h
  /usr/include/t3/wait_group.h
  /usr/lib/libt3.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libt3.pc

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.0.0-1bl2 -----
Rebuild with gcc-13.4.0

----- version 1.0.0-1bl1 -----
